        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Suppliers will be asked to provide costs for things such as TUPE and transition, however these will not be used as part of the evaluation.  They will only be used for financial planning purposes.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
