        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Heritage CMS 2012 system switched to incremental documentation back in 2013.  The high level architecture artefacts have been updated, however, high level designs and low level designs have been oriented around releases or collections of changes.   Part of the DOS Transition / exit planning will address knowledge handover including refresh of relevant documentation.  For new services architecture and design content is up to date and low level deployment details contained within Infrastructure As Code.
